'''Lalli''' is a [[troll]] cook that guards the [[Golden Apple Tree]]. He is needed in [[The Fremennik Trials]] to get the [[golden wool]] required to make the [[enchanted lyre|lyre]]. He seems to be constantly paranoid that the player wants to steal his golden apples. Lalli is the only known troll cook who does not eat humans. He is fooled by the player and a [[pet rock]] during this quest.

He can be reached quickly by using the [[fairy ring]] {{fairycode|AJR}} to get to the [[Rellekka Slayer Caves]]. Slower methods include using the [[enchanted lyre]] to teleport to the [[Rellekka]] area or by teleporting to a [[player-owned house]] (if set to Rellekka or with a [[Rellekka teleport]]).

==Stock==
After the quest, the [[golden fleece]] can be bought for 1000 [[coins]] each from him.
